All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Main
    The Main class contains a main method that tests various inputs for a Test class.
    Password1
    The Password1 class contains methods for checking if a password is balanced, a palindrome, has a minimum length of 8, and contains at least 2 brackets.
    Password2
    The Password2 class contains methods to check if a given integer can be divided exactly by a set of denominations and to check if the integer is within a certain range.
    Test
    The Test class contains a method that checks the validity of a given username, password1, and password2 based on certain criteria.
    Username
    The Username class checks if a given username is valid and if it is contained in a given password.
